commit.message: Clean the test id() more fully
The test that leaves tmpdirs has to also clean up the tmpdirs
Name the temp directory with the id() of the test
The temp directory will be kept if you want
Pytest changed the name of the cache directory
Set show_stderr to let stderr display during tests
Forgot to make make_file part of the API. v1.2.1
Refactor make_file into a global that can be used outside of tests
Refactor module cleanup so we can do it outside of a test
A way to get a quick test
Move test classes to make their use more uniform
Remove behavior checking code that will never run
Move an assertion to before the failure, so it will run
Refactor some class_behavior code, and test it
